name: Sylvia's Framed Doodle
description: This mid-career design is one of Sylvia's doodles, as she worked she would find calmness in drawing simple shapes, exploring where the line would take her. As she explored the patterns in her own life, they would take shape and form on paper. Sylvia’s creative design work was heavily inspired by nature; her prints often evoke imagery of the world around her.
